                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;I&amp;#39;m Julie! And I am thrilled to introduce myself as your new Wellness Concierge at 10X Health! I&amp;#39;m here to provide you with exceptional support and ensure a seamless, high quality experience throughout your wellness journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A little about me:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;With over 20 years in healthcare,I&amp;#39;ve found my passion in functional medicine, helping others achieve their best health. As a wellness concierge at 10X Health, I work alongside my sister, Dr. Carrie Carda, to guide individuals on their journey to optimal well-being. My role is the perfect fit because nothing brings me greater fulfillment than helping people become the best version of themselves.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;I am dedicated to understanding your unique needs and collaborating with your care team to deliver the precise, personalized care you deserve. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If you have any questions or feedback, don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reach out. I&amp;#39;m here to help elevate your wellness experience every step of the way! I look forward to working with you and helping optimize your wellness journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Feel free to book a call with me&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://calendly.com/jcarda-coleman/10x-health-vip-check-in&quot;&gt;https://calendly.com/jcarda-coleman/10x-health-vip-check-in&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In health,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
